{"tid":1532424,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一手fact checked] 教你點樣洗甩螢光粉","createTime":"2019-09-02T13:54:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:38:05.000Z","uid":259173,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"f7da31d6b046b4d6bc670929be2f4d0cdf455f40","tid":1532424,"uid":259173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:54:56.000Z","msg":"頭先見到有po話有螢光粉，咁當然第一時間去照照啦<br />\n照一照真係有！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGnuDQ8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGnuDQ8.jpg&h=a3b0ce2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身見唔大滴，量又唔多，都係喺手臂度，所以去咗沖涼就算<br />\n點知！沖完涼就出事，成身都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲變哂一絲絲纖維咁嘅樣，照燈再睇仲明顯過未沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即刻試下搵椰油捽勻全身，搵毛巾抹一抹，再重覆沖涼嘅步驟<br />\n今次沖完就甩咗好多，效果好顯著，之後會再咁樣沖多次涼！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡單咁講，我估<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好似落妝咁，搵油溶咗啲螢光粉再搵水沖洗！</span></span><br />\n歡迎大家幫手fc！P牌仔推唔到po，求幫推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92dd4a2d4d5e73a0e70cb38c780f4c5d79fd661a","tid":1532424,"uid":259173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734e6382f4304da90b4a42f3975c3a5306a6c786","tid":1532424,"uid":259173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:56:59.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a661050410cbff213b12ed213334071ca9acfea","tid":1532424,"uid":259173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T13:57:29.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10777d7fbd37cb77808e40733319ce9834570daf","tid":1532424,"uid":259173,"like":0,"dislike":0,